commit.message: Remove from main.h functions already declared in options.h
Move opt declaration into options.c and remove useless optarg declaration

Create options module

This commit moves all option related code out from main and into the
option module (options.{c,h}), to ease maintenance.
Make illegal-options related variables local

Streamline option parsing code

This commit tries to untangle the previous complex option parsing code
and simplify flow control understanding.

Besides, the `-m` option does not accept only the first letter of the
desired mode (c, i or t) anymore, as it was not documented and it
presented a potential for errors as users mistyped the mode.
Add SPDX short identifiers for files on project root
Add SPDX short identifiers for files in contrib/
Add SPDX short identifiers to the C source files
